OL,3,CSouthport killer's brother says school
OL,4,Cexpulsion increased his 'isolation'
OL,6,FThe expulsion of the Southport killer
OL,7,Ffrom school in 2019 led to him
OL,8,F"becoming progressively more isolated
OL,9,Ffrom his friends and family," his
OL,10,Fbrother has said.
OL,12,FThe murders had caused the "most
OL,13,Fimmense pain, anguish and grief to the
OL,14,Flives of so many people," said Dion,
OL,15,Fthe brother of AR - as the killer is
OL,16,Fbeing called at the public inquiry
OL,17,Finto the knife attack on 29 July last
OL,18,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
