OL,3,CSouthport killer's brother says school
OL,4,Cexpulsion increased his 'isolation'
OL,6,FAR, now aged 18, killed Alice da Silva
OL,7,FAguiar, nine, Bebe King, six, and
OL,8,FElsie Dot Stancombe, seven, and
OL,9,Fattempted to murder 10 others in the
OL,10,Fattack on a Taylor Swift-themed dance
OL,11,Fclass for young girls.
OL,13,FHe was jailed for life with a minimum
OL,14,Fterm of 52 years.
OL,16,FIn a written statement published to
OL,17,Fthe inquiry, Dion's legal team said it
OL,18,Fwas "plain" he was "wholly unlike" his
OL,19,Fbrother and was a thoughtful young man
OL,20,Fof good character, who was studying at
OL,21,Funiversity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
