OL,3,CSouthport killer's brother says school
OL,4,Cexpulsion increased his 'isolation'
OL,6,FThe statement said: "From Dion's
OL,7,Fperspective, AR's expulsion from
OL,8,Fschool in October 2019 (and the
OL,9,Freasons behind that exclusion) plays
OL,10,Fan important part in AR becoming
OL,11,Fprogressively more isolated from his
OL,12,Ffriends and family.
OL,14,F"Dion anticipates that the inquiry
OL,15,Fwill want to examine the actions of
OL,16,Fthe organisations and agencies who
OL,17,Fdealt with AR after AR was expelled to
OL,18,Fconsider whether there were any other
OL,19,Factions that could have been taken to
OL,20,Ftry and help AR lessen AR's increasing
OL,21,Fdetachment from society.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
