OL,4,Cexpulsion increased his 'isolation'
OL,6,FAt the time of the attack Dion was
OL,7,Fstudying mathematics at the University
OL,8,Fof Warwick. He returned home the
OL,9,Fweekend before the attack, which
OL,10,Fhappened on a Monday.
OL,12,FThe statement added that Dion
OL,13,F"wholeheartedly supports the inquiry's
OL,14,Faim to identify lessons which will
OL,16,Fminimise the prospect of such harm
OL,17,Fbeing caused in the future."
OL,19,FAs a wheelchair user, Dion would not
OL,20,Fbe attending the hearings in person
OL,21,Fbut would follow proceedings remotely.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
